# NWConnection.SendCompletion.contentProcessed(_:)

**Case**

Provide a completion handler that’s invoked when the sent data is processed by the stack.

## Declaration

```swift
@preconcurrency case contentProcessed((NWError?) -> Void)
```

## Completions

- **NWConnection.SendCompletion.idempotent**: Mark the sent data as idempotent—data that can be sent multiple times.
